OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for fourth time in four months
OL,6,FA major hospital has declared the
OL,7,Fhighest alert level for the fourth
OL,8,Ftime in four months.
OL,10,FRoyal Lancaster Infirmary has
OL,11,Fannounced it has gone into Opel 4 due
OL,12,Fto "high demand and pressure" and a
OL,13,Fhigh number of patients with severe or
OL,14,Furgent conditions.
OL,16,FThe hospital said the alert allows
OL,17,Fthem "to be able to take additional
OL,18,Fsteps to maintain safe services for
OL,19,Four patients and help us cope with the
OL,20,Fsignificant and growing demand we are
OL,21,Ffacing."
