OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for fourth time in four months
OL,6,FIn a statement released at the end of
OL,7,FDecember, the University Hospitals of
OL,8,FMorecambe Bay NHS Foundation Trust
OL,9,Fsaid they are "at risk of not having
OL,10,Fthe required money in the bank by
OL,11,FJanuary 2026 to pay the things we need
OL,12,Fto".
OL,14,FAs a result they say this is "leading
OL,15,Fto some very serious decisions around
OL,16,Fthings like what beds we can provide,
OL,17,Fwhat amount of elective activity we
OL,18,Fdo, and what we can and can't pay for."
