OL,3,CMajor hospital declares highest alert
OL,4,Clevel for fourth time in four months
OL,6,FWestmorland and Lonsdale MP Tim Farron
OL,7,Fsays the news proves it is "madness"
OL,8,Fto cut hospital beds.
OL,10,FHe said: "It's absolute madness to be
OL,11,Fclosing beds at a time when pressure
OL,12,Fand demand at Royal Lancaster
OL,13,FInfirmary is at the highest level.
OL,15,F"Patients are already waiting hours in
OL,16,Fpain to be seen at A&E. How on earth
OL,17,Fcan the Government justify cutting
OL,18,Ffunding for our hospitals trust which
OL,19,Fis leading them to cut bed numbers?
