OL,6,F"That's why the Government must U-turn
OL,7,Fand must do so now."
OL,9,FOpel 4 (Operational Pressures
OL,10,FEscalation Level 4) is the highest
OL,11,Falert level in the NHS, signifying
OL,12,Fthat a hospital or local health system
OL,13,Fis under severe pressure and unable to
OL,14,Fdeliver comprehensive care
OL,16,FThe hospital previously declared Opel
OL,17,F4 on 27 October 2025 due to "increased
OL,18,Fpressure".
